description:
Tatsumiya Island`s Core. Daughter of Kouzou Minashiro and younger sister to Soushi Minashiro.
She was born as a core shortly after her mother, Saya Minashiro, was assimilated during the experiment. She teaches Mir what is the meaning of life and death and later sacrifices herself to merge with the newborn core of Tatsumiya Island.
name: Minashiro Tsubaki
